-- Portugal 2020 Bonds Garner Half Level of Interest Shown for October Sale
-- B y   M a t t h e w   B r o w n
-- 2010-11-10T10:51:22Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-10/portugal-2020-bonds-garner-half-level-of-interest-shown-for-october-sale.html
Portugal sold 686 million euros of
bonds maturing in June 2020, with investors bidding for 2.1
times the securities offered, compared with a bid-to-cover ratio
of 4.9 in September, according to government data.  To contact the reporter on this story:
